The name 'Washington' refers to several places in the United States. Most
commonly it refers to one of the following:

*Washington (state), a state on the Pacific coast. *Washington, D.C., the
capital city of the United States. **The Washington Metropolitan Area.

'Washington' may also refer to:


* Washington, Arkansas
* Washington, Nevada County, California
* Washington, Yolo County, California
* Washington, Connecticut
